race.comment: WOOLGOOLGA (1) had a low draw last time over 400m at Bulli but was in traffic and fell. Given another chance here. RITZA BENJI (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (22.91) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Expected to feature. LITTLE BIT SUPER (3) finished fourth last time at Bulli but could not have been more impressive before that in her exceptional 19.08 win at Bulli over 340m. Should be in this for a long way. CHA CHA ETHICS (4) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 2.25 lengths away in second (17.73). Overdue and gets her chance.
